<p><a name="Synopsis" id="Synopsis"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=The_Power_of_Nightmares&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Synopsis">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Synopsis</span></h2>
<div class="thumb tleft">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:288px;">
<table style="background: transparent; border: 0; padding: 0; margin: 0; width:284px;" cellspacing="0">
<tr>
<td style="padding: auto; margin: 0;" class="thumbimage"><a href="/wiki/File:Wolfowitz_press_briefing,_Nov_2001.jpg" class="image" title="Paul Wolfowitz and Ayman al-Zawahiri, featured representatives of Neo-Conservatism and Islamism respectively."><img alt="Paul Wolfowitz and Ayman al-Zawahiri, featured representatives of Neo-Conservatism and Islamism respectively." src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/eb/Wolfowitz_press_briefing%2C_Nov_2001.jpg/135px-Wolfowitz_press_briefing%2C_Nov_2001.jpg" width="135" height="199" border="0" /></a></td>
<td style="padding: 0; margin: 0; border: 0; width: 2px"></td>
<td style="padding: auto; margin: 0;" class="thumbimage"><a href="/wiki/File:Ayman_al_Zawahiri.jpg" class="image" title="Paul Wolfowitz and Ayman al-Zawahiri, featured representatives of Neo-Conservatism and Islamism respectively."><img alt="Paul Wolfowitz and Ayman al-Zawahiri, featured representatives of Neo-Conservatism and Islamism respectively." src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a9/Ayman_al_Zawahiri.jpg/145px-Ayman_al_Zawahiri.jpg" width="145" height="193" border="0" /></a></td>
</tr>
<tr style="vertical-align:top;">
<td style="padding: 0; margin: 0; border: 0;" colspan="3">
<div class="thumbcaption"><a href="/wiki/Paul_Wolfowitz" title="Paul Wolfowitz">Paul Wolfowitz</a> and <a href="/wiki/Ayman_al-Zawahiri" title="Ayman al-Zawahiri">Ayman al-Zawahiri</a>, featured<br />
representatives of Neo-Conservatism and Islamism respectively.</div>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
